> Parse milliseconds into an object
> This Module wrapper for parse-ms


## Install

```
$ npm install parse-ms-js
```


## Usage

```js
parseMsJS(1337000001);
/*
{
	days: 15,
	hours: 11,
	minutes: 23,
	seconds: 20,
	milliseconds: 1,
	microseconds: 0,
	nanoseconds: 0
}
*/
```
